
## Implementation

- File: `Makefile`
- Add CLAWQ_BIN variable defaulting to ./_build/default/src/main.exe
- Add `restart` target: $(CLAWQ_BIN) service signal-restart
- Add `build-restart` target: depends on build and restart

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] `make restart` sends signal-restart to running daemon
- [ ] `make build-restart` builds then restarts (end-to-end dev loop works)
- [ ] Targets appear in `make help` output (if help target exists)
